articles.title: About this blog
articles.description: Some additional details about the blog
articles.contents:
Hi there, in this blog, I explore COVID-19 situation in Japan by conducting analysis on the number of death, number of postive case of COVID-19, COVID-19 in different prefecture in Japan, Vaccination status and recovery rate. If this is something that interests you, you are welcome continue to explore my blog and contact me by my email:
email: qxuu0023@student.monash.edu
